      <div class="ds-row ds-row-3 row clearfix" id="section-overview">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 ds-region-r3c1">
          
<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><h2>How can our Berkeley school help you learn English?</h2>

<p>Our English school in Berkeley is located downtown and just 20 minutes from San Francisco. The school offers a range of English courses that will help you develop your English in the way you need.</p>

<ul><li>Sign up for an English course that works around your schedule with a<a href="/flexible-english-courses">flexible-length English course</a>available for 2 weeks or more</li>
	<li>Invest more time in your education with a five, six or nine month English course</li>
	<li>Prepare for TOEFL, GMAT or GRE exams to help your future career with an<a href="/exam-preparation-courses">English exam preparation course</a></li>
</ul><h2>What is great about Berkeley?</h2>

<ul><li>Berkeley is a city with a traditional academic atmosphere, lots of green spaces and is an ideal community for international students</li>
	<li>Students at Berkeley also gain access to the the Kaplan<a href="/university-placement-service" target="_blank">University Placement Service</a>, which can help you get into graduate and undergraduate university courses around the country using our academic network</li>
</ul><p></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact-us/form" style="line-height: 20px; padding: 10px 50px 10px 50px;line-height:15px;">CONTACT AN ADVISOR<br /><font style="font-size:10px;">FOR MORE INFORMATION</font></a></p>

<p><a href="/brochure-download/form"><u>DOWNLOAD FREE KAPLAN BROCHURE</u></a></p>

<p></p>

<p>We also offer E<a href="/united-states/san-francisco/berkeley-young-learners">nglish courses for young learners in Berkeley</a></p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>
        </div>
      
