<div class="field field-name-field-school-facilities field-type-double-field field-label-above">
      <h3 class="field-label">School facilities</h3>
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><div class="double-field-accordion"><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-classroom"></span><a href="#">Classrooms</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Our English schhol in Berkeley has 10 well-equipped modern classrooms, all fitted with interactive whiteboards</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-whiteboard"></span><a href="#">Interactive white boards</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Interactive whiteboards are able to incorporate various media forms like video and audio which can enhance the English learning experience</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-wifi"></span><a href="#">WiFi</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Available throughout the school</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-study"></span><a href="#">Study Center</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Large study area with individual cubicles, 15 computers with internet access and online language learning resources. There are also TVs, DVD players and headphones</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-library"></span><a href="#">Library</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Wide variety of textbooks, dictionaries, materials for additional practice and as part of the K+ learning system</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-lounge"></span><a href="#">Student Lounge</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Includes eating area, plus a lounge with a TV, Wii and a foosball table. There is also a quiet and comfortable prayer room for student use.</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-cafe"></span><a href="#">Cafeteria</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">There is no on-site cafeteria, but there is a kitchen with a refrigerator, microwave and filtered water</div></div><div class="accrd-row"><h3><span class="icon icon-ki-faci-transport"></span><a href="#">Transport</a></h3><div class="accrd-detail">Berkeley has an extensive transportation system including local bus lines and a train system (BART) that services the East Bay, San Francisco and local airports</div></div></div></div>
      </div>
</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
