<p>Our schools in California are approved to operate as an accredited institution by the California Bureau for Private Post-secondary Education <a href="http://www.bppe.ca.gov/" target="_blank">(bppe.ca.gov)</a>.Take a look at our<a href="/privacy#toc-california-state-disclosures38" target="_blank">California State Disclosures list</a>for the documents filed with the state and/or required to be made available to students prior to enrollment.</p>

<p><em>This school is authorized under Federal law to enroll nonimmigrant alien students.</em><em>All courses offered by Kaplan International are avocational and recreational, and are not intended to lead to vocation, occupation or career opportunities. Kaplan International does not confer credits, certification, diploma or degree for any courses, and no credits are transferrable to institutions of higher education.</em></p>

